List of network requirements, and VMs

This diagram contains all the VMs I am planning to include, along with detailed information like IP addresses, VLANs, subnets, etc.

VMs needed:

- Firewall
- Malware Analysis (MA) VMs (one for Linux and one for Windows)
- Windows 7 host
- Windows 10 host
- Windows Server AD
- Linux Server(s)
- Kali Linux
- DFIR
- SIEM
- Vulnerability Scanner

Services that will be implemented:

- Antivirus
- EDR/XDR
- Proxy
- Mail Server
- AD Services
- IDS/IPS
- Monitoring
- Docker
- Database (not sure yet what kind of, but will think about it)

